question: Where can I find restaurant as you head towards Neil Carey Arena, IL from Gabis Arboretum at Purdue Northwest, Valparaiso, IN, within a radius of 120 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-87.149569 41.444803)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-88.082005 41.605308)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-87.149569 41.444803)',4326)::geography, 120000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-87.149569 41.444803)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
